{"tid":2423032,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中大要求新當選學生會幹事會註冊為獨立社團或公司","createTime":"2021-02-25T15:39:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T17:48:59.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c477a4a878e83d063134de56f94c207afbdb8a31","tid":2423032,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577563-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577563-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6w%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=c5865d37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577563-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9ed35c3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577563-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中大學生會幹事會候選內閣「朔夜」昨日當選，中大晚上發出嚴正聲明，指當選內閣政綱內容不代表大學立場，又指幹事會經勸喻後並未澄清相關言論，決定暫停為學生會代收學生會會費，原有由學生會幹事會所提供的學生服務如受影響，將由學生事務處跟進。中大亦要求學生會註冊為獨立社團或公司，自行承擔法律責任。<br />\n<br />\n中大亦決定，暫停學生會幹事會相關學生在校內不同委員會的職務；亦暫停校方為學生會幹事會提供的行政與大學場地支援。學生會附屬組織向大學領取津貼及其他財政支援安排，則不受影響 。<br />\n<br />\n中大表示，校方本3日曾發出聲明，強烈反對內閣發表的參選宣言及接受媒體訪問時言論，亦與相關學生溝通，針對國家安全的言論，有可能違法。中大指，學生會幹事會內閣成員對大學的失實指控，及利用校園作政治宣傳平台，違背了大學宗旨，令大學聲譽受損。<br />\n<br />\n中大重申，絕不容許校園出現危害國家安全的事。若學生作出煽動違法言論，大學將予以嚴厲處分，包括着令有關學生暫時停學或將有關學生開除。<br />\n<br />\n「朔夜」早前在參選宣言中指，《港區國安法》成為極權高壓統治的政治手段，又指中文大學向政權低頭，報警拘捕中大學生等。"},{"pid":"88804d9ef66dc4b955493f66c6e6d366a6be729a","tid":2423032,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中大晚上發出嚴正聲明，指當選內閣政綱內容不代表大學立場</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜嘢政綱搞都又要拉又要鎖？"},{"pid":"8dd0ecf64f2ffff0bd47bbf2b731052525f6ec31","tid":2423032,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"跪得唔好睇都係犯法<br />\n這就是香港，很好的人權"},{"pid":"4d1eab38bad9aa1b9f1c78eef594cc50a96f5a51","tid":2423032,"uid":117037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"想知政綱係乜要搞到咁大"},{"pid":"989ca8cd9c3badde1912e1302def25783719f2c0","tid":2423032,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:43:57.000Z","msg":"中大班友, 之前唔係段爸, 段爸咁既咩?<br />\n<br />\n你地個段爸去咗邊呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌, 真係毛管戙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4126e9db6cc16ab6c1c1d44419cde881be03097e","tid":2423032,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:49:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">段狗死全家</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daec20d0407878adf22edba7c60be3e255384c4","tid":2423032,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"中大 = TVB <br />\n<br />\n朔夜 = 用廣東話接受ATV訪問既歌手"},{"pid":"69833661973360122082b0542cb19779fbad205e","tid":2423032,"uid":226851,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c477a4a878e83d063134de56f94c207afbdb8a31","tid":2423032,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577563-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577563-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd6w%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=c5865d37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577563-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9ed35c3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577563-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中大學生會幹事會候選內閣「朔夜」昨日當選，中大晚上發出嚴正聲明，指當選內閣政綱內容不